  | Accordion supports the following sizes: <code>sm</code>, <code>md</code> (default), <code>lg</code>, and <code>xl</code>.
.example.-mb--3#example3
  .-p--3.-p-lg--6
    each size in ['sm', 'md', 'lg', 'xl']
      p.-text--bold.-pl--2= size
        div(class=`chi-accordion -${size}` id=`example-size-${size}`)
          .chi-accordion__item
            button.chi-accordion__trigger
              i.chi-icon.icon-chevron-down
              .chi-accordion__title
                | Accordion
            .chi-accordion__content
              p.chi-accordion__text Content goes here
  .example-tabs.-pl--2
    ul.chi-tabs#example-accordion-sizes
      li.-disabled
        a(href=`#webcomponent-accordion-sizes`) Web Component
      li.-active
        a(href=`#html-accordion-sizes`) HTML Blueprint
  .chi-tabs-panel#webcomponent-accordion-sizes
  .chi-tabs-panel.-active#html-accordion-sizes
    .chi-tab__description
      span.-text--grey
        | This HTML Blueprint requires JavaScript.
        | You may use your own solution, or use Chi's vanilla JavaScript solution,
        | <a href="../../getting-started/installation">Chi.js</a>.
    :code(lang="html")
